4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>♡ Traps ♡</strong><br><br><br><br></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Take advantage of holy tools imbued with sacred power. Set clever traps tailored to each ghost’s personality and desires. Once they fall into your snare, you’ll be free to… do all sorts of naughty things with them…</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3987800/extras/44d7783a58faf0c5a0cb84d86e8e4fca.poster.avif?t=1776826877\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3987800/extras/44d7783a58faf0c5a0cb84d86e8e4fca.webm?t=1776826877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3987800/extras/44d7783a58faf0c5a0cb84d86e8e4fca.mp4?t=1776826877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>♡ The “Redemption” Ritual ♡</strong><br><br><br><br></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ghosts are embodiments of concentrated negative energy. The most effective way to heal them is from within. Once you’ve broken their will to fight, step in as the exorcist to begin the “Redemption” ritual, curing them thoroughly from the inside out!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3987800/extras/21689e3216d245c1e5b47d0e279fe70a.poster.avif?t=1776826877\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3987800/extras/21689e3216d245c1e5b47d0e279fe70a.webm?t=1776826877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3987800/extras/21689e3216d245c1e5b47d0e279fe70a.mp4?t=177